RelationalDataCollection class

RelationalDataCollection.Rd

Abstract class containing code for handling set of datasets. This cannot be created directly. Use either RelationalDataConnector (for a set of datasets to be pulled from an external source) or RelationalData (for a set of datasets to be passed into a teal application)

Cannot create a RelationalDataCollection object Create a RelationalData or
RelationalDataConnector object instead

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$new()

Returns

throws error

Method check()

Check if the object raw data is reproducible from the get_code() code.

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$check()

Returns

NULL if check step has been disabled TRUE if all the datasets generated from evaluating the get_code() code are identical to the raw data, else FALSE.

Method get_check_result()

Get result of reproducibility check

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$get_check_result()

Returns

NULL if check has not been called yet, TRUE / FALSE otherwise

Method get_code()

Get code for all datasets.

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$get_code(dataname = NULL, deparse = TRUE)

Arguments

dataname

(character) dataname or NULL for all datasets

deparse

(logical) whether to return the deparsed form of a call

Returns

(character) vector of code to generate datasets.

Get internal CodeClass object

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$get_code_class(only_pull = FALSE)

Arguments

only_pull

(logical value)
if TRUE only code to pull datasets will be returned without mutate code.

Returns

CodeClass

Method mutate()

Mutate data by code

Usage

RelationalDataCollection$mutate(code, vars = list())

Arguments

(character) Code to mutate the dataset. Must contain the dataset$dataname

vars

(list)
In case when this object code depends on the raw_data from the other RelationalDataset, RelationalDatasetConnector object(s) or other constant value, this/these object(s) should be included

Returns

self invisibly for chaining
